 Firefox\n   3. ☑ MacVim\n   4. ☑ Claude\n   5. ☑ Quicksilver\, launch on s
 tartup/login\n   6. ☑ Emacs railwaycat\n      1. ☑ Install missing package
 s (only a few)\n3. ☑ Setup eduroam\n4. ☒ Install apps/software to match "o
 ld" work device\n   1. ☑ +pdftk+\, use Preview instead\n   2. ☑ Zoom\n   3
 . ☑ OneDrive\n   4. ☐ Inkscape\n   5. ☐ GIMP\n   6. ☐ ApE\n   7. ☐ Fiji\n5
 . LaTeX\n   1. ☐ MacTeX\n6. ☒ Helper apps\n   1. ☑ Goodnotes\n   2. ☑ PDF 
 Viewer\n   3. ☑ Hidden Bar\n   4. ☑ Rectangle\n   5. ☒ BetterDisplay: DCC 
 issue via HDMI\n   6. ☑ Skim (PDF)\n   7. ☐ HazeOve\n7. ☐ Fun\n   1. ☐ Wha
 tsApp\n   2. ☐ Spotify\n   3. ☐ Radio Garden
